title: Ravens revitalized after 23-20 overtime win against Steelers
text:
> Sports Ravens revitalized after 23-20 overtime win against Steelers Baltimore Ravens kicker Justin Tucker (9) kicks the game winning field goal in overtime of an NFL football game against the Pittsburgh Steelers, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015 in Pittsburgh. The Ravens won 23-20 in overtime. (AP Photo/Gene J. Puskar)
